@startuml
title Submit Assignment Activity Diagram
|Student|
start
:View Assignment Details;
|System|
if (Submission Open?) then (Yes)
    |Student|
    :Click "Submit";
    :Select File to Upload;
    :Confirm Submission;
    |System|
    :Upload File;
    :Create Submission Record;
    :Show Success;
else (No)
    :Show "Late" or "Closed" Status;
    stop
endif

stop
@enduml
